Global Heat Shock Protein Beta 1 Market Insights
Heat Shock Protein Beta 1 Market size was valued at USD 0.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.2 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 12.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Heat Shock Protein Beta 1 Market Overview
The Heat Shock Protein Beta 1 (HSPB1) market has witnessed significant growth, with its market value reaching approximately USD 1.5 billion in 2024. This market is driven by increasing demand in the pharmaceutical and biotechnology sectors, particularly for the treatment of diseases related to protein misfolding, such as neurodegenerative disorders. Ongoing research and clinical trials exploring the therapeutic potential of HSPB1 also contribute to the market's expansion. The market is expected to grow at a CAGR of 6.5% from 2024 to 2030, making it a rapidly developing area within the biotechnology industry.

