Asia-Pacific
The Asia-Pacific region is anticipated to exhibit the highest growth rate, driven by emerging biotechnology sectors and increasing healthcare investments in countries like China and India.
Latin America
Latin America’s market is expanding due to rising awareness of biotechnology advancements, though challenges remain in terms of accessibility and affordability.
Middle East & Africa
The Middle East and Africa are experiencing growth as healthcare facilities improve and more clinical trials are conducted in the region, increasing HSPB1 market penetration.
